## Rust codeblocks

This contains various examples of codeblocks, specific to rust

### Simple

```rust
fn main(){
    println!("Hello world!");
}
```

### With Hidden lines

```rust
# fn main(){
    println!("Hello world!");
# }
```

### Editable

```rust,editable
fn main(){
    println!("Hello world!");
}
```
